TextEng: Any news that you can tell me of?
For a small inn, the place sure seems busy.
I'd like to ask you about this competition of yours.
How about a room?
I'll be going.
Why are Luskan's gates closed?
Is that why the inn is so busy?
There wouldn't be some *other* reason, would there?
The patrons seem to say that something else is going on.
Text: 손님들은 뭔가 다른 일이 벌어지고 있다고 말하던데요.

TextEng: I'd like to know some more about it, first.
Text: 먼저 그것에 대해 더 알고 싶은데요.

TextEng: What's the reward?
Yes, I'd like to take part.
No. Not interested.
I think your contest is barbaric!
Could you explain all that again?
You gots news for me?
Why so busy? All people here to sleeps?
Text: 왜 이렇게 바빠? 다들 자러 온 거야?

TextEng: Me gots question about you competition.
Me wants to get a room, please.
Me goes bye.
Thank you. It was quite the experience.
Me says thanks for gold. Dungeon was good.
Text: 나 금화 고맙다고 말해. 던전 좋았어.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Come on? That's it? Throw in another 300.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me do good! Me gets... 300 gold more?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 잘했어! 나 받아... 금화 300개 더?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> How about just 200 gold more?
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me gets 200 more, me goes away.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Make it 100 more, and I'll leave satisfied.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me just wants 100 gold is all! Please?
I want more gold, and I'm taking it.
Me wants more gold! Now! Me takes! Now!
Text: 나 금화 더 원해! 지금! 나 가져가! 지금!

TextEng: Bye.
Why is gates to Luskan is closed?
So that is why inn so busy?
That only reason is so busy? No other reason?
Me hears other say some things different.
Text: 나 다른 사람들 다른 말 하는 거 들었어.

TextEng: Yes. Me do this.
Tell more. Me not know what is it.
Text: 더 말해. 나 그게 뭔지 몰라.

TextEng: What happens if me wins? What me get?
Text: 나 이기면 뭐 생겨? 뭐 받아?

TextEng: No, me is not doing this.
Me not hear all you say. Say again?
Text: 나 네 말 다 못 들었어. 다시 말해?

TextEng: Me think you make people as animal! Meanie!
Text: 나 생각엔 너 사람들 동물처럼 만들어! 나쁜 사람!

TextEng: You're right. Tell me about your contest, then.
Okay. Me re-thinks. Say about contest, then.
Text: 좋아. 나 다시 생각했어. 대회 말해줘.

TextEng: Me wants to see goods.
Let me see your goods.
Let me see what you sells.
Let me see what you're selling.
